{"tid":2094662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電話騙案】「我係國安公署打黎，你個仔畀人扣查，揾人送伙食費過來畀你個仔。」","createTime":"2020-07-04T22:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T12:42:54.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e391f33d9c006ec4b5d6cf1da26db409a3e1790b","tid":2094662,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T22:16:46.000Z","msg":"2020-07-04 2230 #港區國安法 #武警<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本共同社引述消息說，北京將派遣200至300名武警以觀察員身份駐港。<br />\n<br />\n國安公署人員有必要時將會在示威、遊行及集會現場在高姿態巡邏，必要時作出扣查或拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國安公署人員可帶走任何被警方拘捕的疑犯，而一貫的48小時扣留上限將不適用。<br />\n<br />\n國安公署不必遵從被捕人律師向法院申請的人身保護令。<br />\n<br />\n被捕的人數及其姓名，將不會對家屬或全傳媒通布。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1329030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1329030&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=12f58a0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1329030</a>"},{"pid":"2ab3e6af7753bc4ca012986f78663cebf94b0070","tid":2094662,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T22:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307060a1ac9f76c4f5069a69abebb98798dfceda","tid":2094662,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T22:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc6ff43963dca4a7504cb7b7eb9feff2ce0f72b","tid":2094662,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T23:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1eb6c43ee702e54cd105f0acf24e35f72b754c4","tid":2094662,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}